overview: Having caught her son's friend messing with her panties, Francesca finds a suitable punishment for the young perv. Real estate agent Jewels Jade will do anything to sell a house, even if it means getting her hands dirty. Julia Ann tries to be neighborly when she sees Dane having relationship problems. A chance encounter has Mariah fulfilling Michael's longtime fantasy. Nikki needs a date to make her ex husband jealous and is offering a handsome reward for a job well done.
title: Cougar's Prey 5
